Megatron Revived:
 
Hearing Rodimus say it was alright to come in, the door slid open and the larger white and  black bot stepped inside.  His gaze immediatly fell upon the small femme and then shifted to Rodimus.
 
"I thought I may contribute to your planning session against Unicron."

Dark Mouse <raccoon7679@...> wrote:
Silence::

She made the slightest movement that show almost no indication that
the buzzer startled her.  She tilted her head to make the mental not
not to let her guard down, even in her new home.  She sighed slightly,
but tenced up at the new energy signature.  She turned in her seat to
face the door to see who it was about to enter. 


"HA!  Is that all you got?  You boasted such power, such skill!  Where is your power and skill now?  You disappoint me, ha ha ha haa!"
